@node Bugs "BeSel - Known bugs"
@next Author
@prev History

  @{b}Known bugs@{ub}
  ----------

  No bugs found yet, although probably does not work on Draco etc.

  If you find any, contact the @{" author " link Author}.
  (Feel free to correct my bad English.)

  BeSel has been tested on the following configurations:

  - A3000, '030, OS 3.1, 14MB, 640MB, Merlin Gfx
  - A3000, '030, OS 2.1, 14MB
  - A3000, '030, OS 1.3, 2MB
  - A500, '000, OS 3.1/1.3, 7MB, 1.2GB

  This program was tested with Enforcer, Mungwall and
  Spot-A-Bug-Gizmo.

@endnode

